age, hypothecation, or any other form of asset pledge.\\n\\n9. Loan Cancellation and Refund: This section explains the process for loan cancellation, the circumstances under which a loan may be canceled, and the refund policy for any prepaid amounts or interest paid.\\n\\n10. Grievance Redressal: This section outlines the process for addressing customer grievances, including the channels for raising complaints (e.g., phone, email, or in-person), the timeframe for resolution, and the escalation process if the issue"}, "sources": [{"object": "context.chunk", "score": 0.6815138482262668, "document": {"object": "ingest.document", "doc_id": "ed43bc06-1189-44de-b1c6-c46ae1971f6b", "doc_metadata": {"window": "C. Procedure ai mentioned in openint of new lir\\u20acd deposlt account and dellvery of tixed Deposit Receipt\\nshould be followed in case offixed depositrenewal.\\n D. Custome/r requert and the originalFixed Deposit Receipt of m atur\\u20acd [ixed deposltshould be keptin the\\ncustome/s account opening file.\\n ln case customer want5lo withdraw the amount in FixEd Deposit b\\u20acfor\\u20ac maturity, staff at CSo shallexplain about\\nthe possible loss ol interest to th!  customer, The customer should be counseled to take loan egainst Fixed Deposit\\nto avoid possible loss in case ol premature liquidation ofthefixed deposit.\\n Eranch sha ll follow proced ures as follows for premature llquldation ol flxed deposit:9+A.  fhe customer muJt proyiden req.uert in wrltlns and submit the orlAlnalFired DeDosit Receipt.  h case ol\\ncompany, a board mif'Illr'o?irrJr6{6re riqutaitton orthe rixed de-posit shoutd be obtained.\\n", "original_text": "customer, The customer should be counseled to take loan egainst Fixed Deposit\\nto avoid possible loss in case ol premature liquidation ofthefixed deposit.\\n", "page_label": "35", "file_name": "Unified Branch Operations Manual.pdf", "doc_id": "ed43bc06-1189-44de-b1c6-c46ae1971f6b"}}, "text": "C. Procedure ai mentioned in openint of new