 data accuracy, and gain better visibility into your working capital position.\\n\\n9. Continuously improve: Regularly review and analyze your working capital management practices and identify areas for improvement. Stay up-to-date with industry best practices and regulatory requirements.\\n\\n10. Seek professional advice: Consult with financial advisors, accountants, and other experts to ensure you are following best practices and making informed decisions about your working capital management strategy."}, "sources": [{"object": "context.chunk", "score": 0.680238790901859, "document": {"object": "ingest.document", "doc_id": "dd36c155-e473-4300-a6db-be3ec62b8128", "doc_metadata": {"window": "Central Trade Operations that look after international trade shall remain \\nalert regarding various risks related to documents - inconsistencies, \\ndiscrepancies, missing documents to identify the trade-based money \\nlaundering. \\n a. Be vigilant with the customer exhibiting changes in current patterns \\nfollowed by a customer: \\ni. Abnormal shipping routes in comparison to the practice \\npreviously followed by the applicant or by others known to the \\nBank. \\n \\n ii.  Letter of credit by placing 100% cash margin in cases except \\nmandatorily required by the policy of the Bank or by \\nregulators. \\n \\n iii.  Letters of credit are frequently amended. \\n \\n iv. ", "original_text": "Letter of credit by placing 100% cash margin in cases except \\nmandatorily required by the policy of the Bank or by \\nregulators. \\n \\n", "page_label": "36", "file_name": "AML CFT Guideline 2023 (2).pdf", "doc_id": "dd36c155-e473-4300-a6db-be3ec62b8128"}}, "text": "Central Trade Operations that look after international trade shall remain \\nalert regarding various risks related to documents - inconsistencies, \\ndiscrepancies, missing documents to identify the trade-based money \\nlaundering. \\n a. Be vigilant with the customer exhibiting changes in current patterns \\nfollowed by a