ional resources and counseling to borrowers on financial management, budgeting, and repayment strategies to help them make informed decisions and manage their debt responsibly.\\n10. Regular review and monitoring: Conduct periodic reviews of the borrower's financial situation and adjust loan terms as needed to ensure that they remain affordable and manageable throughout the repayment period."}, "sources": [{"object": "context.chunk", "score": 0.6908314485650014, "document": {"object": "ingest.document", "doc_id": "dd36c155-e473-4300-a6db-be3ec62b8128", "doc_metadata": {"window": "ii.  Letter of credit by placing 100% cash margin in cases except \\nmandatorily required by the policy of the Bank or by \\nregulators. \\n \\n iii.  Letters of credit are frequently amended. \\n \\n iv.  Significant discrepancies in description, value, quality or \\nquantity of goods apparent on official documents (invoices, \\nbills of lading, etc.). \\n \\n b. Any transaction in which the nature, size or frequency appears \\nunusual \\ni. A customer suddenly starts to trade in high volumes of high \\nvalue goods. \\n \\n", "original_text": "Letters of credit are frequently amended. \\n \\n", "page_label": "36", "file_name": "AML CFT Guideline 2023 (2).pdf", "doc_id": "dd36c155-e473-4300-a6db-be3ec62b8128"}}, "text": "ii.  Letter of credit by placing 100% cash margin in cases except \\nmandatorily required by the policy of the Bank or by \\nregulators. \\n \\n iii.  Letters of credit are frequently amended. \\n \\n iv.  Significant discrepancies in description, value, quality or \\nquantity of goods apparent on official documents (invoices, \\nbills of lading, etc.). \\n \\n b. Any transaction in which the nature, size or frequency appears \\nunusual \\ni. A customer suddenly starts to trade in high volumes of high \\nvalue goods. \\n \\n", "previous_texts": null, "next_texts": null}, {"object": "context.chunk", "score": 0.6867698860113827, "document": {"object": "ingest.document", "doc_